{"tid":701711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：《蘋果》奪SOPA卓越視頻大獎","createTime":"2018-06-14T10:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T10:34:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"76720159bc579b5109b12f4cb493d9e091d30872","tid":701711,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:34:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180614/20420245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180614%2F20420245&d=sX8bL84bYpOGpKt1KXoOY8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=580f1d0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180614%2F20420245&h=bd0b10e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180614/20420245</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月14日 <br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：《蘋果》奪SOPA卓越視頻大獎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180614/large/a10a02a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180614%2Flarge%2Fa10a02a.gif&h=e5721363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《蘋果》記者及攝影師憑報道孤兒雜技團（右圖）奪本年度SOPA卓越視頻報道大獎。　<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n《蘋果日報》喺噚晚舉行嘅2018年亞洲出版業協會（SOPA）頒獎禮入面，憑着去年到河南濮陽採訪中國孤兒雜技團嘅報道，奪得卓越視頻報道大獎，台灣《蘋果日報》獲相同組別獲得銀獎，成為香港同台灣《蘋果》首次包辦SOPA卓越視頻報道獎。八方都喺度恭喜得獎嘅同事。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》去年到稱為中國雜技之鄉嘅河南濮陽，採訪當地一個「孤兒雜技團」，講述團長劉甫曾坐牢，出獄後行善專收留孤兒或單親家庭、窮困家庭小孩，甚至殘疾兒童練雜技。記者直擊團中23名5歲半至15歲孩童，描繪23個被遺棄嘅故事（<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2sSC2Mj）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2sSC2Mj%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=sX8bL84bYpOGpKt1KXoOY8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=47cb7a26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2sSC2Mj）。</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與台蘋包辦首次名<br />\n<br />\n台蘋就憑採訪台灣發明家嘅勵志故事（<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Mmi4Sk），喺相同組別中奪得銀獎。此外，台蘋拍攝羅興亞難民危機喺孟加拉邊境持續蔓延，（http://www.appledaily.biz/rohingya），西方政府與媒體一面倒同情難民處境，其中一張照片奪得卓越攝影大獎。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Mmi4Sk%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%96%BA%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E7%B5%84%E5%88%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%A5%AA%E5%BE%97%E9%8A%80%E7%8D%8E%E3%80%82%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%B0%E8%98%8B%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D%E7%BE%85%E8%88%88%E4%BA%9E%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F%E5%96%BA%E5%AD%9F%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%89%E9%82%8A%E5%A2%83%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E8%94%93%E5%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%EF%BC%88http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.biz%2Frohingya%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%88%87%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E4%B8%80%E9%9D%A2%E5%80%92%E5%90%8C%E6%83%85%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E8%99%95%E5%A2%83%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%B5%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E5%A5%AA%E5%BE%97%E5%8D%93%E8%B6%8A%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E5%A4%A7%E7%8D%8E%E3%80%82&d=sX8bL84bYpOGpKt1KXoOY8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=b2919edd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Mmi4Sk），喺相同組別中奪得銀獎。此外，台蘋拍攝羅興亞難民危機喺孟加拉邊境持續蔓延，（http://www.appledaily.biz/rohingya），西方政府與媒體一面倒同情難民處境，其中一張照片奪得卓越攝影大獎。</a>  <br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：託友人fb報平安　游BB獄中繪笑臉：I am fine (李八方)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：傳轉投建制　政壇李克勤：無中生有 (李八方)"}]}